parameters.name: filter
parameters.description:
Example Filter: ``{
	bot:		true,		// AppBot or SystemBot
	cm:			true,
	owner:		true,
	event:		true,
	online:		true,
	inChannel:	true,
	away:		true,
	developer:	true,
	status:		[
					Status.Newbie,
					Status.Family,
					Status.Stammi,
					Status.Ehrenz,
					Status.Admin,
					Status.Sysadmin,
					Status.Bot
				],
	gender:		[
					Gender.Male,
					Gender.Female,
					Gender.Unknown
				]
}``
